{"tid":1560467,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(9.12 魔法重生) 魔域戰記 Abigail","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:05:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T23:19:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9d1a97ee27dd224bd82a86267e80fde3fbc377","tid":1560467,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:05:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wmoov.com/assets/movie/photo/201908/FB_IMG_1565496045897_1565603155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwmoov.com%2Fassets%2Fmovie%2Fphoto%2F201908%2FFB_IMG_1565496045897_1565603155.jpg&h=4a453e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演 :<br />\n    Aleksandr Boguslavskiy<br />\n<br />\n演員 :<br />\n    Tinatin Dalakishvili, Eddie Marsan, Rinal Mukhametov<br />\n<br />\n片長 :<br />\n    1小時51分<br />\n<br />\n級別 :<br />\n    IIA 級<br />\n<br />\n語言 :<br />\n    英語 (中英文字幕)<br />\n<br />\n上映 :<br />\n    12.9.2019 (公映) <br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌所居住的城鎮，自古以來邊界都被政府嚴密封鎖，以防市民感染某種神秘的致命病毒。阿嬌小時候父親不幸染病被捉走，只剩下兩母女相依為命。長大後的她誓要救出父親，可惜一直苦無他法。<br />\n<br />\n直至遇上革命軍貝爾，在大本營裡她發現城市曾充斥著不可思議的魔力、精靈及一群可操控魔法的「天才」。政府的鎖國政策原來只是為囚禁市民的策略，而致命病毒也只是為了瞞騙市民魔力的謊言。與此同時，阿嬌身上的魔力逐漸被喚醒，但因為革命軍的身份被政府追捕。自由無價，阿嬌只有挑戰政權勢力才能找出父親下落，等待她的是無數強敵和重重難關，還要面對人性及愛情的抉擇......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nnJKooMkvnI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnnJKooMkvnI&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWSpZd1NrJsyKidS%2BVLva3MM%3D&h=00dc4801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nnJKooMkvnI</a>"},{"pid":"4fadc29dfe23292ec1690d42fcdc28108e18f259","tid":1560467,"uid":58526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:09:15.000Z","msg":"伏撚到仆街<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"eae8b19a49c1dbe41235a91486f410f5636eb734","tid":1560467,"uid":34074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:21:24.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"0436f25ab4b65bab9d6444fbfc094f305163f5a2","tid